Class AttributeUser

  • soap.local.entity.SOAPBaseType
    • soap.local.entity.GWObject
      • soap.local.entity.AttributeUser

  • public class AttributeUser
extends GWObject
    Links an Attribute entity with a User entity. An Attribute is a general-purpose characteristic you can associate with one or more users.
